{"tid":636271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當局拘禁申請抗議美國貿易戰示威者","createTime":"2018-04-20T16:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T06:31:38.000Z","uid":22876,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2840bec7b7355a4acc2dc4c7c493c021ffc5df06","tid":636271,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/zmmy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Fzmmy.jpg&h=83560e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易紛爭在中國網絡引發沸沸揚揚討論。有網民對美國向中國發動貿易戰憤慨，向警方申請遊行，表達對美國抗議立場。南京一位居民申請示威遭拒絕後卻失蹤。中國官方嚴控各種理由的示威遊行申請。<br />\n<br />\n據東方日報今天報道，中美貿易戰煙硝味愈來愈濃之際，有中國內地民眾打算趁「五一勞動節」，以遊行方式表達自己訴求，向當局提交遊行集會申請表後卻不獲批准。江蘇南京異見人士王健欲於下月1日，組織反對美國發動貿易戰的遊行，他本月16日向警方提交申請表，豈料翌日起突然失蹤。有傳王健被指「涉嫌尋釁滋事罪」遭拘留。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述境外傳媒報道，自王健失蹤當天，其家人及朋友撥打王的電話，但都一直未能接通。報道引述王健的友人表示，王希望在五一勞動節組織隊伍遊行，主題包括反對美國發動貿易戰及為勞工爭取權益等。不過，王健周一到南京市公安局提交遊行申請書後，卻於翌日接到警方電話後被帶走。警方18日又到其住所取走電腦等物品。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，也有內地其他民眾申請在下月1日時示威遊行，但同樣不獲准許。"},{"pid":"03d8fb977a324fce76d88c3766184b191c6069ba","tid":636271,"uid":22876,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"美國又出招！ 擬引緊急權力法限制中國投資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpZYZ9Er.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpZYZ9Er.jpg&h=59944770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美中貿易戰美國頻頻出招，外媒報導，有官員指出，美財政部將援引《國際緊急經濟權力法》限制中國對美投資，料與知識產權有關。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，美國財政部助理部長Heath Tarbert在國際金融協會論壇表示，財政部關於限制中國投資的特別辦公室，正在考慮推動美國外資審議委員會對外資審查的改革，或是運用《國際緊急經濟權力法》，以有助於川普政府對301條款知識產權的補救。<br />\n<br />\n先前《紐約時報》便曾報導，1977年的《國際緊急經濟權力法》（International Emergency Economic Powers Act）曾在911攻擊後，用於對其他國家進行制裁。該法賦予總統權力，能夠取消商業交易和凍結外國資產。<br />\n<br />\n美國外資審議委員會則負責審查國際併購，可建議總統阻止對國家安全構成威脅的外國投資。"},{"pid":"0d5b2738d0160d2bcaa3c1e42ce1c84a130e846a","tid":636271,"uid":41545,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T19:11:16.000Z","msg":"支那人成日都當自己係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆一次大型遊行你唔驚黎多次八國聯軍共匪都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比你班畜牲咁做分分鐘真係滅國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531267c708bb90cfdb2f2a83b32483723e903058","tid":636271,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:05:18.000Z","msg":"噶"},{"pid":"801d175a6880dad0ac73ea91f0a0b84d63031b4d","tid":636271,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:11:04.000Z","msg":"當自己人民係咩"},{"pid":"1911981af68e8139f2e5637cc3af1583f8da3c71","tid":636271,"uid":102179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"當年啲反韓示威唔見你咁做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1df58b1700f0b0fbe10f5add16ac2ed6f565d7","tid":636271,"uid":5715,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"江蘇南京異見人士王健欲於下月1日，組織反對美國發動貿易戰的遊行，他本月16日向警方提交申請表，豈料翌日起突然失蹤。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619a2b256c43cc74fa5a664cbfa9c6c48a42734c","tid":636271,"uid":12449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:45:52.000Z","msg":"你班中國人係敵對嘅美國到先敢遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國人咁痛恨美國<br />\n政府點知你地舉辦嘅反美示威會唔會演變成暴亂<br />\n搶劫店鋪或者打爛街上面嘅汽車<br />\n釣魚台反日都有例子啦<br />\n所以唔批准都好合理"},{"pid":"67bb48423420ac1d6a3505085e0d127fc3d1f635","tid":636271,"uid":10438,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"支那仔本身諗住今次可以搶iPhone <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4e2f8c55e921ba7acc2c205c791311974b74b3","tid":636271,"uid":43173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1911981af68e8139f2e5637cc3af1583f8da3c71","tid":636271,"uid":102179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"當年啲反韓示威唔見你咁做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"你唔喺諗住反韓反日示威真係民間自發呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894e482b1d291bb712ba0215c0493c67ed3c6fb1","tid":636271,"uid":338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf4e2f8c55e921ba7acc2c205c791311974b74b3","tid":636271,"uid":43173,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1911981af68e8139f2e5637cc3af1583f8da3c71","tid":636271,"uid":102179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"當年啲反韓示威唔見你咁做既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"你唔喺諗住反韓反日示威真係民間自發呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal